    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing the pinnacle of automotive care. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, showroom-quality shine with no scratches, dents, or chips whatsoever. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery and trim looking as if they just rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. This car offers a like-new driving experience and is ready for a collector or an enthusiast who demands the very best.",
