    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in pristine, showroom condition. Every aspect of the vehicle, from its flawless exterior finish to its immaculate interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. Mechanically superior and aesthetically perfect, this vehicle is suited for the most discerning collector or enthusiast seeking uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
