    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute dream of a car. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still feels like it just left the showroom! It's in spectacular shape inside and out\u2014seriously, you have to see it to believe how pristine it is. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a pinnacle of BMW's M-Division engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, producing a high-revving 333hp with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical provenance is impeccable: the critical rod bearing recall has been addressed, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, feeding power through a refreshed limited-slip differential. The suspension features a precision-aligned setup with Bilstein PSS10 coilovers and polyurethane bushings for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no evidence of orange peel or swirl marks. This is a zero-fault, mechanically sorted masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Original paint. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Full service history.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, thanks to a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing, the carpets are spotless, and it has never been smoked in. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized service centers\u2014all records are included. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is exceptionally clean, reflecting its history as a fair-weather weekend driver. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-quality vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Includes original window sticker, all manuals, and two sets of keys.",
      "price": 48500.0,
